\nhigher magnetizations. We finally show that reconnection in pair-proton plasmas\nwith multiplicities $\\kappa \\sim 1-20$, magnetizations $\\sigma \\sim 1-10$, and\ntemperatures $\\Theta_e \\sim 1-10$ results in particle power law slopes and\naverage electron Lorentz factors that are consistent with those inferred in\nleptonic models of AGN jet emission.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 7 Jun 2019 18:57:11 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-07-31"}
